    "baseEffectDescription": "<p style=\"text-align: justify\">When creating a magical creature, the Magic Might of the creature cannot exceed the level of the spell, and requisites must be included for any special powers (for example, Ignem if it can breathe fire, Rego and Mentem if it can control people's minds). A Vim requisite, for the magical nature, is always required.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">Such spell always have Vim requisite, for the beast's magic, and normally have other requisites for its powers.</p>",
